      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has proven to be a reliable daily driver over the years. While the engine starts and the car is fully drivable, it does show clear signs of its age and mileage, including some minor cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior. Buyers can expect a solid, functional vehicle that may require some routine maintenance or minor fluid top-offs to keep it in peak operating form. It is a practical choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an affordable price point.",
