    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as intended, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
