    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolute pristine, mint condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single blemish to be found! I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I've priced it to be a total steal for anyone wanting a basically-new ride without the new-car price tag. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
